r the Mac OS X Dashboard, inspired by real car dashboards. Size: 250.71 KB.</P>\r\n<P><IMG style=\"BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px\" height=124 alt=dasbboard src=\"http://techmagazine.ws/wp-content/uploads/2007/11/dasbboard.jpg\" width=260 border=0>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P><A href=\"http://jonas.seph.ws/index.html\" target=_blank rel=nofollow>Danish Royalty Free Icons</A> by Jonas Rask: is an icon set of 32\u00d732 pixel toolbar icons. You can use them in your apps, in your toolbar, on your website. A credit would be appreciated greatly, but it\u2019s not obligatory at all. Package includes ICNS,PNG, TIFF, Mac Icons and Pixadex iContainer versions.</P>\r\n<P><IMG style=\"BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px\" height=153 alt=raskdesign src=\"http://techmagazine.ws/wp-content/uploads/2007/11/raskdesign.jpg\" width=400 border=0></P>\r\n<P><A href=\"http://www.zeusbox.org/blog/feedicons\" target=_blank rel=nofollow>Feedicons</A> is an iconset from Zeus Box Studio. You may use them to give your \u201csubscribe to RSS-feed\u201d-button a fresh look.</P>\r\n<P><IMG style=\"BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px\" height=203 alt=feedicons src=\"http://techmagazine.ws/wp-content/uploads/2007/11/feedicons.jpg\" width=243 border=0></P>\r\n<P><A href=\"http://icons.alanwho.com/104-standard-pc-keyboard-keys-icon-set/\" target=_blank rel=nofollow>104 standard PC keyboard key icons</A>: feel free to to copy, distribute, display, and perform the work entitled \u201c104 Standard PC Keyboard Key\u2019s Icon Set\u201d for both non-commercial and commercial purposes. You are also free to make derivative works.</P>\r\n<P><IMG style=\"BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px\" height=231 alt=keyboard src=\"http://techmagazine.ws/wp-content/uploads/2007/11/keybo